description: The Sony WH-1000XM4 is a top-of-the-line over-ear headphone with industry-leading noise-canceling technology. With exceptional sound quality, long battery life, and touch controls, it's a favorite among audiophiles and travelers. The comfortable design and smart features make it an excellent choice for immersive audio experiences.

The Bose QuietComfort 35 II is a popular over-ear headphone known for its superb noise-canceling capabilities. With a balanced sound profile and comfortable fit, it's a great companion for long listening sessions and travel. The QC 35 II offers voice assistant integration and customizable settings through the Bose Connect app.

The Sennheiser HD 660 S is a high-end over-ear headphone designed for audiophiles seeking exceptional sound quality. With an open-back design, these headphones deliver a natural and transparent audio experience. The HD 660 S is ideal for critical listening and home use, providing comfort and precision.

The Apple AirPods Pro is a premium in-ear headphone with active noise cancellation and a customizable fit. Featuring a compact design and seamless integration with Apple devices, the AirPods Pro deliver immersive sound and adaptive EQ. The transparency mode adds versatility for awareness of surroundings.

The Beyerdynamic DT 990 Pro is a reliable over-ear headphone known for its open-back design and detailed audio reproduction. With a comfortable fit and durable construction, the DT 990 Pro is favored by audio professionals and enthusiasts. The headphones provide a spacious soundstage for critical listening.

The JBL Free X is a true wireless headphone offering a cord-free experience for on-the-go users. With Bluetooth connectivity and a compact charging case, these earbuds are convenient and lightweight. The JBL Free X provides reliable sound quality and hands-free calling for an active lifestyle.
